        "second_richtext": "<h2>UK & Europe Shipping</h2><p>We’re excited to bring Pawcredible nutrition to dogs across the UK and Europe, here’s how our shipping works.</p><p><strong>Order Processing</strong></p><ul><li>Orders are packed and dispatched within 1-3 business days (Monday–Friday, excluding public holidays).<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Shipping Options</strong></p><p><strong>UK Mainland (DPD Next Day)</strong></p><ul><li>£5.40 per parcel (Unless order is over £70)<br/></li><li>Delivery time: 1 working day once dispatched<br/></li><li>Tracked delivery with DPD Predict (1-hour delivery window)<br/></li><li>Available for all UK mainland postcodes.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Europe Shipping (DPD Classic)</strong><br/><br/>Delivery times vary by destination. Rates below are per parcel:</p><p><strong>Belgium, France, Germany, Luxembourg, Netherlands</strong></p><ul><li>£17.39 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: typically 3–5 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Austria, Denmark, Switzerland</strong></p><ul><li>£16.93 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: typically 3–6 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Czech Republic, Italy, Slovakia, Spain</strong></p><ul><li>£16.09 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: typically 4–7 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Croatia, Estonia, Finland, Hungary, Poland, Portugal, Slovenia, Sweden</strong></p><ul><li>£27.33 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: typically 4–8 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Bulgaria, Greece, Latvia, Lithuania, Norway, Romania</strong></p><ul><li>£30.69 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: typically 5–10 business days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Ireland Shipping</strong></p><p><strong>Republic of Ireland (DPD Two-Day Service)</strong></p><ul><li>£10.06 per parcel<br/></li><li>Delivery: 2 working days<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Offshore UK Shipping</strong></p><ul><li>Channel Islands (Two day) — £15.96 per parcel<br/></li><li>Northern Ireland (Next day) — £20.19 per parcel<br/></li><li>Northern Ireland (Two-day) — £9.69 per parcel<br/></li><li>Scottish Islands (Two-day) — £11.15 per parcel<br/></li><li>Scottish Highlands (Two-day) — £11.15 per parcel<br/></li><li>Isle of Man (Two-day) — £11.73 per parcel<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Free Shipping Threshold</strong></p><ul><li>Free standard shipping on UK orders over £70 (Available for all UK mainland postcodes only.)<br/></li><li>(Express shipping rates still apply if you choose faster delivery.)<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Customs & Import Duties (EU Orders)</strong></p><ul><li>Customers are responsible for any import VAT, duties, or customs fees applied by their country.<br/></li><li>We provide estimates at checkout, but final charges depend on local regulations and may be collected at delivery.</li></ul>",
